CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: biopsy-medsiglip-probe (L4b)', id: 'arbiter_model:biopsy_medsiglip_probe', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: biopsy-medsiglip-probe (L4b)\n\n**Version**: `biopsy_probe_v0` (2026-07-03)\n**Backbone**: `google/medsiglip-448` (HAI-DEF gated, requires HF_TOKEN + accepted terms)\n**Head**: linear (3-class) + Platt temperature scaling\n**Status**: **RESEARCH USE ONLY** — NOT FDA cleared. Weights are **synthetic**.\n\n## Intended use\n\nGiven a breast biopsy image (WSI patch or gross photo), return one of ', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/biopsy_medsiglip_probe.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card errata — `oncology-arbiter`', id: 'arbiter_model:errata', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card errata — `oncology-arbiter`\n\nThis file tracks corrections and updates to the model cards under\n`docs/model_cards/`. Every entry MUST include (a) the affected card,\n(b) the change, (c) the source URL and fetch date, and (d) the commit\nthat introduced the correction.\n\n## Schema\n\n```\n### YYYY-MM-DD — <card slug>\n\n- **Change**: <what was fixed / added>\n- **Source**: <URL, fetch date>\n- **', 'ruo_marker_present=False'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/errata.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Frontend SPA (React + Vite)', id: 'arbiter_model:frontend_spa', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Frontend SPA (React + Vite)\n\n**RESEARCH USE ONLY** — not for diagnostic use. See `RUO_DISCLAIMER` in `oncology_arbiter/__init__.py`.\n\nThe oncology-arbiter frontend is a single-page React application served\noptionally by the FastAPI backend under `/ui/`. It calls only the documented\n`/v1/*` and `/health` endpoints — it holds no clinical logic, no thresholds,\nand no risk-tier assignments of its ow', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/frontend_spa.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: `google/medgemma-27b-it` (MedGemma 1 27B multimodal)', id: 'arbiter_model:medgemma_1_27b', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: `google/medgemma-27b-it` (MedGemma 1 27B multimodal)\n\nSource-of-truth: same MedGemma model card as MedGemma 1.5 4B, which reports\nMedGemma 1 27B numbers as a comparison baseline for the 1.5 4B release.\n\n## Identifiers\n\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| HuggingFace repo | `google/medgemma-27b-it` |\n| Model version | 1.0.x (MedGemma 1 line; not yet updated to 1.5) |\n| Key publication | Med', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/medgemma_1_27b.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: `google/medgemma-1.5-4b-it`', id: 'arbiter_model:medgemma_1_5_4b', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: `google/medgemma-1.5-4b-it`\n\nSource-of-truth model card:\n<https://developers.google.com/health-ai-developer-foundations/medgemma/model-card>\n(fetched into this repo\'s `execution_trace/transcript.jsonl`; all numeric\nvalues below come from that source unless flagged as our own measurement).\n\n## Identifiers\n\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| HuggingFace repo | `google/medgemma-1.5-4b-it` |\n', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/medgemma_1_5_4b.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: `google/medsiglip-448`', id: 'arbiter_model:medsiglip_448', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: `google/medsiglip-448`\n\nSource-of-truth model card:\n<https://developers.google.com/health-ai-developer-foundations/medsiglip/model-card>\n(fetched into this repo\'s `execution_trace/transcript.jsonl`; all numeric\nvalues below come from that source unless flagged as our own measurement).\n\n## Identifiers\n\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| HuggingFace repo | `google/medsiglip-448` |\n| Model v', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/medsiglip_448.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: monai-detector-heuristic (L4a)', id: 'arbiter_model:monai_detector_heuristic', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: monai-detector-heuristic (L4a)\n\n**Version**: `monai-detector-heuristic-v0` (2026-07-03)\n**Backbone**: MONAI `transforms` (SpatialCrop, GaussianSmooth) + Sobel edges\n**Head**: connected-components + non-max suppression on gradient hotspots\n**Status**: **RESEARCH USE ONLY** — NOT FDA cleared. `weights_loaded=False`.\nHeuristic mode ONLY under this build.\n\n## Intended use\n\nGiven a prepro', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/monai_detector_heuristic.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model Card — NSCLC Lung Heuristic + NCCN-lite (Oncology Arbiter v0.2)', id: 'arbiter_model:nsclc_lung_heuristic_v0', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model Card — NSCLC Lung Heuristic + NCCN-lite (Oncology Arbiter v0.2)\n\n**Model name (wire):** `nsclc_lung_heuristic_v0+nccn_nsclc_lite_v0`\n**Model state (wire):** `proxy_lung_heuristic`\n**Intended use:** Research / demonstration only.\n**Not for use:** Diagnosis, screening, therapy selection, or any clinical decision. **Not FDA-cleared.**\n\n## 1. What this actually is\n\nThis card describes the NSCL', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/nsclc_lung_heuristic_v0.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card — report_parser_clinicalbert_v1', id: 'arbiter_model:report_parser_clinicalbert_v1', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card — report_parser_clinicalbert_v1\n\n## Summary\n\nToken-classification head fine-tuned on top of `emilyalsentzer/Bio_ClinicalBERT`\nto extract 11 entity types from breast-cancer pathology reports and roll them\nup into the schema used by `oncology_arbiter`\'s regex parser. Used inside the\nfused-mode report parser to rescue reports where the regex layer fails on\nlong-form or non-standard phras', 'ruo_marker_present=False'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/report_parser_clinicalbert_v1.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: `google/siglip-base-patch16-224` (ungated public SigLIP proxy)', id: 'arbiter_model:siglip_base_patch16_224', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: `google/siglip-base-patch16-224` (ungated public SigLIP proxy)\n\nThis is the **public, ungated** SigLIP checkpoint used by `oncology-arbiter`\nas a smoke-test proxy when the gated `google/medsiglip-448` cannot be\naccessed. It is a general-domain SigLIP, NOT a medical model.\n\n## Identifiers\n\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| HuggingFace repo | `google/siglip-base-patch16-224` |\n| Model fami', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/siglip_base_patch16_224.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: therapy-nccn-lite (L4c fallback)', id: 'arbiter_model:therapy_nccn_lite', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: therapy-nccn-lite (L4c fallback)\n\n**Version**: `nccn-lite-v0` (2026-07-03)\n**Type**: **Deterministic rules-based lookup** — NOT a machine learning model.\n**Source guideline**: NCCN Guidelines Version 2.2025 — Invasive Breast\nCancer / DCIS, `https://www.nccn.org/professionals/physician_gls/pdf/breast.pdf`.\n**Status**: **RESEARCH USE ONLY** — NOT FDA cleared, NOT for clinical\ndecision-', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/therapy_nccn_lite.md'});
CREATE (:Entity:ArbiterModel:KBNode {product_layer: 'tumor_board', cross_refs: ['regulatory_posture:oncology_arbiter_ruo'], mint_planner: 'p3', stream: 'v3:audit_upgrade', attributes_json: '{}', name: 'Model card: txgemma-9b-chat (L4c primary — currently gated)', id: 'arbiter_model:txgemma_9b_chat', type: 'arbiter_model', verbatim: ['# Model card: txgemma-9b-chat (L4c primary — currently gated)\n\n**Repo**: `google/txgemma-9b-chat` (HAI-DEF gated)\n**Backup repo**: `google/txgemma-9b-predict`\n**Status under current session token (2026-07-03)**: **HTTP 403 FORBIDDEN**.\nThe token `HF_TOKEN=hf_SfwLOG…` has NOT accepted the HAI-DEF terms for\nTxGemma. Preflight refuses to load weights; endpoint falls through to the\nNCCN-lite rules pro', 'ruo_marker_present=True'], source_file: 'scientist-monai-moat/docs/model_cards/txgemma_9b_chat.md'});
